name: dogecast
description: Dogecast is a token inspired by Elon Musk and Vivek Ramaswamy's weekly podcast committed to government transparency, apart of, the Department Of Government Efficiency, "DOGE" in the USA. Dogecast stands as a symbol of innovation and change in both the crypto space and public administration. Vivek Ramaswamy has said 2 times that they will call it Dogecast on his X account, and Elon Confirmed that they will do it weekly on his X account. Vivek liked our tweet asking about Dogecast.
